gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Pacers 132, Rockets 129
gameRecap.excerpt: The Pacers defeated the Rockets, 132-129. Pascal Siakam recorded 29 points, four rebounds, and four assists for the Pacers, with Tyrese Haliburton adding 18 points and seven assists in the victory. Jalen Green tallied 30 points (3-5 3PM) and three rebounds for the Rockets in the losing effort. The Pacers improve to 29-23, while the Rockets fall to 23-27.
